.SH NAME
shelly-cover-position - Set cover position


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly cover position   [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Set a cover/roller component to a specific position.

.PP
Position is specified as a percentage from 0 (closed) to 100 (open).


